# KB Academy Permissions Foundation

## Base Roles
- Admin
- Manager
- Supervisor
- Team Lead
- Operator
- Trainer
- Team Member
- FSQA
- People Services

## Permission Strategy
KB Academy uses:
- base role templates
- configurable permission matrix
- user-level overrides
- feature toggles such as trainer-enabled access

