## Role Intent
### Admin
Full access.

### Manager
Broad operational and reporting access with settings access as configured.

### Supervisor
Department-focused user, training, certification, and place chart access.

### Trainer
Training delivery, hour logging, and trainee support access.

### Team Lead
Operational distinction with configurable permissions.

### Operator
Own training and limited operational visibility.

### Team Member
Own training only.

### FSQA
Compliance and training-related access for quality workflows.

### People Services
Read-only or reporting-focused people data access.

